Erwin Lemmens, the national team's goalkeeping coach: &quot;Karius was no better than Simon a year ago, and it was not fair to have a less good goalkeeper than him in his place. I supported Simon a lot at the World Cup (in 2018). Being present in this great tournament did him good.&quot;<br />
<br />
Lemmens: &quot;The time has come to leave. I'm sure he'll find a good club. He must regain the pleasure of playing.&quot;
